About:
yamli4xchat is a plugin to be used with XChat IRC Client, simply it use Yamli.com to convert arabic/english words to arabic words..

---

Installation:
First, make sure you have the following 2 perl modules before using this plugin:
* LWP::Simple
* JSON 

All what you have to do now is to load yamli4xchat.pl file in XChat client (Window --> Plugins and Scripts --> Add)

---

Usage:
In the messeges tab, write /ya and whatever.. for example:

/ya alsalam 3lykom

<ME>  السلام عليكم

---

Warning:
This created as testing and just for fun, so don't expect it works as you expect (between its slow!) 
